text: Glencora McGhie (born 8 August 1988) is an Australian water polo player. She was part of the Australian team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships and 2016 FINA Women's Intercontinental Tournament. == References == == Other websites == * Water Polo - 16th FINA World Championships: Day Fourteen zimbio * Water Polo - 16th FINA World Championships: Day Two getty Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Australian water polo players
